sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant Ctrl as InventoryController
    participant Svc as InventoryService
    participant Repo as InventoryRepository
    participant FS as IFileStorage
    participant MR as IMediaRepository
    participant DB as Database

    Note over C,DB: Stock Out from Dish Prep: POST /api/inventory/transactions (TypeLvId=OUT, ExportReasonLvId=COOKING)

    C->>+Ctrl: POST /transactions (CreateInventoryTransactionFormRequest)
    Note right of Ctrl: RequestJson contains TypeLvId=OUT, ExportReasonLvId=COOKING, Items=[ingredients used]
    Ctrl->>Ctrl: Deserialize RequestJson
    Ctrl->>Ctrl: GetCurrentUserId()
    Ctrl->>Ctrl: MapFiles(EvidenceFiles)
    Ctrl->>+Svc: CreateTransactionAsync(request, userId, evidenceFiles, ct)

    Svc->>Svc: Resolve DRAFT status via LookupResolver
    Svc->>Svc: ResolveTypeCodeAsync(TypeLvId) returns OUT
    Svc->>+Repo: GetTodayTransactionCountByTypeAsync(OUT, ct)
    Repo->>+DB: COUNT WHERE TypeCode=OUT AND today
    DB-->>-Repo: count
    Repo-->>-Svc: count
    Svc->>Svc: GenerateTransactionCodeAsync -> OUT-YYYYMMDD-SEQ

    Svc->>+Repo: CreateTransactionAsync(transaction, items, ct)
    Repo->>+DB: INSERT InventoryTransaction (type=OUT, status=DRAFT, exportReason=COOKING)
    DB-->>-Repo: TransactionId
    Repo->>+DB: INSERT InventoryTransactionItems (ingredients with quantities)
    DB-->>-Repo: ok
    Repo-->>-Svc: transactionId

    opt Evidence files provided
        Svc->>+FS: SaveManyAsync(uploadRequests, inventory-evidence, ImageUpload, ct)
        FS-->>-Svc: uploadResults
        loop Each uploaded file
            Svc->>+MR: AddMediaAsync(MediaAsset, ct)
            MR-->>-Svc: MediaAsset
        end
        Svc->>+Repo: UpdateTransactionAsync(transaction, ct)
        Repo->>+DB: UPDATE (attach media)
        DB-->>-Repo: ok
        Repo-->>-Svc: ok
    end

    Svc->>+Repo: GetTransactionByIdAsync(transactionId, ct)
    Repo->>+DB: SELECT with Includes
    DB-->>-Repo: entity
    Repo-->>-Svc: entity
    Svc->>Svc: MapToDetailDto(entity)
    Svc-->>-Ctrl: InventoryTransactionDetailDto (status=DRAFT)
    Ctrl-->>-C: 200 ApiResponse with InventoryTransactionDetailDto

    Note over C,DB: Submit DRAFT for approval

    C->>+Ctrl: POST /transactions/{id}/submit (SubmitTransactionRequest)
    Ctrl->>+Svc: SubmitTransactionAsync(id, request, userId, ct)
    Svc->>+Repo: GetTransactionByIdAsync(id, ct)
    Repo-->>-Svc: entity (DRAFT)

    Svc->>Svc: ValidateExportReasonScopingAsync - verify COOKING is valid for FOOD_INGREDIENT items

    alt Item category not in allowed set for COOKING
        Svc-->>C: InvalidOperationException
    end

    Svc->>Svc: Set status = PENDING_APPROVAL, SubmittedAt = now
    Svc->>+Repo: UpdateTransactionAsync(entity, ct)
    Repo->>+DB: UPDATE
    DB-->>-Repo: ok
    Repo-->>-Svc: ok

    Svc->>Svc: NotificationService.PublishAsync(INVENTORY_TX_SUBMITTED)

    Svc->>Svc: Return updated detail DTO
    Svc-->>-Ctrl: InventoryTransactionDetailDto
    Ctrl-->>-C: 200 ApiResponse